title: Friends of the Earth Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, International, Macrobiotic, Organic, Juice bar
description: Veggie cafe serving hot vegan organic lunch (a mixed plate with occasional non-vegan vegetarian option), vegan sweets, treats, breads, and muffins. Also a bulk organic grocer with fresh fruit and vegetables, cosmetics, and cleaning products. Enviro bookshop and campaign office on site.
